                <li><b>Java 8 <a href="http://openjdk.java.net/install/" target="_blank">OpenJDK</a>/<a href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html" target="_blank">Oracle</a></b></li>
